# Earnings Call Summary — {ticker} {fiscal_quarter} {fiscal_year}

## 1. Headline numbers
- Revenue (with YoY %)
- EPS, diluted (with YoY %)
- Gross / operating / net margin
- Other guidance-relevant metrics

## 2. Segment performance
- Per-segment revenue, growth, drivers/headwinds

## 3. Management commentary themes
- Growth drivers
- Headwinds / risks
- Strategic priorities

## 4. Forward guidance
- Next-quarter / full-year outlook
- Capital allocation (buybacks, dividends, capex)

## 5. Notable Q&A points
- Top 3-5 analyst questions and management responses

Style: concise bullet points. Quote management verbatim (<=15 words) only when phrasing matters. Cite numbers from the financial results.
